```json
{
  "application": "MPI",
  "details": {
    "scheduler": "PBS",
    "queue": "workq",
    "walltime": "0:10:00",
    "filesystems": "home:tegu",
    "account": "datascience",
    "nodes": 2,
    "software": {
      "conda": "activated",
      "mpiexec": "used",
      "python": "used",
      "torch_nccl": "used",
      "launcher.sh": "used",
      "aws-ofi-nccl": "v1.9.1-aws",
      "hwloc": "used",
      "nccl": "used"
    },
    "environment_variables": [
      "NCCL_NET_GDR_LEVEL=PHB",
      "NCCL_CROSS_NIC=1",
      "NCCL_COLLNET_ENABLE=1",
      "NCCL_NET=\"AWS Libfabric\"",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/soft/libraries/aws-ofi-nccl/v1.9.1-aws/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/soft/libraries/hwloc/lib/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "FI_CXI_DISABLE_HOST_REGISTER=1",
      "FI_MR_CACHE_MONITOR=userfaultfd",
      "FI_CXI_DEFAULT_CQ_SIZE=131072",
      "NCCL_DEBUG=INFO",
      "OUTPUT=logs0/$(date +\"%Y-%m-%d-%H-%M-%S\")",
      "MASTER_ADDR=`hostname`"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "cpu": "4 per node",
      "memory": "not specified",
      "storage": "tegu filesystem"
    },
    "execution_flow": [
      "set up environment variables",
      "activate conda environment",
      "run torch_nccl.py with different MPI configurations",
      "log output to files"
    ]
  }
}
```
